{
  "page": "Frozen Shore",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"thumb tright\">\n<div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:402px;\">\n<div style=\"position: relative; border: 1px solid lightgray\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:The_North.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"The north and the location of the Frozen Shore\"><img alt=\"The north and the location of the Frozen Shore\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/f3/The_North.png/400px-The_North.png\" width=\"400\" height=\"431\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/f/f3/The_North.png/600px-The_North.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/f/f3/The_North.png/800px-The_North.png 2x\" /></a><div style=\"position: absolute; z-index: 2; top: 12.2%; left: 18.6%; height: 0; width: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"><div style=\"position: relative; text-align: center; left: -5px; top: -5px; width: 9px; font-size: 9px;\"><img alt=\"The north and the location of the Frozen Shore\" src=\"/images/thumb/e/ea/Wolff2.PNG/9px-Wolff2.PNG\" title=\"Frozen Shore\" width=\"9\" height=\"9\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/e/ea/Wolff2.PNG/14px-Wolff2.PNG 1.5x, /images/thumb/e/ea/Wolff2.PNG/18px-Wolff2.PNG 2x\" /></div><div style=\"font-size:&#160;%; line-height: 110%; z-index:90; position: relative; top: -1.5em; width: 6em; left: 0.5em; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"padding: 1px;\"><b>Frozen Shore</b></span></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"thumbcaption\">The <a href=\"/index.php/North\" title=\"North\">north</a> and the location of the Frozen Shore\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><table>\n\n<tbody><tr><td></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:352px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:TheFrozenShore_JCBarquet.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/a/af/TheFrozenShore_JCBarquet.jpg/350px-TheFrozenShore_JCBarquet.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"389\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/a/af/TheFrozenShore_JCBarquet.jpg/525px-TheFrozenShore_JCBarquet.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/a/af/TheFrozenShore_JCBarquet.jpg/700px-TheFrozenShore_JCBarquet.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:TheFrozenShore_JCBarquet.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>The Frozen Shore, by Juan Carlos Barquet © Fantasy Flight Games</div></div></div>\n<p>The <b>Frozen Shore</b> or <b>frozen shore</b><sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot17.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot17.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> is the western shore of the lands <a href=\"/index.php/Beyond_the_Wall\" title=\"Beyond the Wall\">beyond the Wall</a>,<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rawoiaffrozen_shore.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rawoiaffrozen_shore.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> with the <a href=\"/index.php/Bay_of_Ice\" title=\"Bay of Ice\">Bay of Ice</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Bear_Island\" title=\"Bear Island\">Bear Island</a> to the south.<sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> An unnamed river with tributaries flows south through the region to the Bay of Ice and the <a href=\"/index.php/Sunset_Sea\" title=\"Sunset Sea\">Sunset Sea</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtloiafwesteros.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtloiafwesteros.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Inhabitants\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Inhabitants</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">History</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#A_Storm_of_Swords\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Storm of Swords</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Quotes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Inhabitants\">Inhabitants</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Frozen_Shore&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Inhabitants\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The <a href=\"/index.php/Men_of_the_Frozen_Shore\" title=\"Men of the Frozen Shore\">men of the Frozen Shore</a> are <a href=\"/index.php/Free_folk\" title=\"Free folk\">free folk</a> who ride sleds pulled by <a href=\"/index.php/Dog\" title=\"Dog\">dogs</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_wall_and_beyond:_the_wildlings.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_wall_and_beyond:_the_wildlings.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup> Some men wear <a href=\"/index.php/Walrus\" title=\"Walrus\">walrus</a> tusks in their hats and others antlers, with the two groups not getting along.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd58.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd58.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Some accounts state gods of snow and ice are worshipped on the Frozen Shore.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_wall_and_beyond:_the_wildlings.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_wall_and_beyond:_the_wildlings.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Frozen_Shore&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The <a href=\"/index.php/Ironborn\" title=\"Ironborn\">ironborn</a> of antiquity controlled the <a href=\"/index.php/Sunset_Sea\" title=\"Sunset Sea\">Sunset Sea</a> from the Frozen Shore to the <a href=\"/index.php/Arbor\" title=\"Arbor\">Arbor</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_iron_islands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_7-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_iron_islands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p><a href=\"/index.php/Wildlings\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Wildlings\">Wildlings</a> from the Frozen Shore have raided <a href=\"/index.php/Bear_Island\" title=\"Bear Island\">Bear Island</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos45.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_8-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos45.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-8\">&#91;8&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>During the reign of King <a href=\"/index.php/Dorren_Stark\" title=\"Dorren Stark\">Dorren Stark</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Redwyn\" title=\"Redwyn\">Redwyn</a> of the <a href=\"/index.php/Night%27s_Watch\" title=\"Night&#39;s Watch\">Night's Watch</a> claimed he encountered <a href=\"/index.php/Giants\" title=\"Giants\">giants</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Children_of_the_forest\" title=\"Children of the forest\">children of the forest</a> while ranging from the <a href=\"/index.php/Shadow_Tower\" title=\"Shadow Tower\">Shadow Tower</a> to <a href=\"/index.php/Lorn_Point\" title=\"Lorn Point\">Lorn Point</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok6.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_9-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok6.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-9\">&#91;9&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafancient_history:_the_dawn_age.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_10-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafancient_history:_the_dawn_age.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-10\">&#91;10&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Before <a href=\"/index.php/Mance_Rayder\" title=\"Mance Rayder\">Mance Rayder</a> negotiated a peace, the <a href=\"/index.php/Men_of_the_Frozen_Shore\" title=\"Men of the Frozen Shore\">walrus men</a> fought with those of the <a href=\"/index.php/Ice-river_clans\" title=\"Ice-river clans\">ice-river clans</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos15.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_11-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos15.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-11\">&#91;11&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Frozen_Shore&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Storm_of_Swords\"><i>A Storm of Swords</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Frozen_Shore&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Storm of Swords\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Mance_Rayder\" title=\"Mance Rayder\">Mance Rayder</a>, the <a href=\"/index.php/King-beyond-the-Wall\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"King-beyond-the-Wall\">King-beyond-the-Wall</a>, tells <a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Snow\" title=\"Jon Snow\">Jon Snow</a> that his cloak of black wool and scarlet silk was a gift from a wildling woman who patched him up. The scarlet silk was her grandmother's most prized possession, which she found in the wreck of a cog from <a href=\"/index.php/Asshai\" title=\"Asshai\">Asshai</a> off the Frozen Shore.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos7.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_12-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos7.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-12\">&#91;12&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p><a href=\"/index.php/Men_of_the_Frozen_Shore\" title=\"Men of the Frozen Shore\">Men of the Frozen Shore</a> are found in Mance's army as it <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_beneath_the_Wall\" title=\"Battle beneath the Wall\">attacks the Wall</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos64.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_13-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos64.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-13\">&#91;13&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes\">Quotes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Frozen_Shore&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p><b>Jon</b>: The <a href=\"/index.php/Great_Walrus\" title=\"Great Walrus\">Great Walrus</a>? Truly?<br />\n<b>Tormund</b>: They have queer names along the Frozen Shore.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd58.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd58.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Snow\" title=\"Jon Snow\">Jon Snow</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Tormund\" title=\"Tormund\">Tormund</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Frozen_Shore&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap mw-references-columns\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Ragot17.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot17.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"A Game of Thrones\">A Game of Thrones</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones-Chapter_17\" title=\"A Game of Thrones-Chapter 17\">Chapter 17</a>, Bran III.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rawoiaffrozen_shore.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rawoiaffrozen_shore.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_World_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\"A World of Ice and Fire\">George R. R. Martin's A World of Ice and Fire</a></i>, Frozen Shore.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Map_of_the_North\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Map of the North\">Map of the North</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtloiafwesteros.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtloiafwesteros.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Lands_of_Ic